Name: Gamma Space
About the game: You play the role of a spaceship surrounded by an asteroid field. Your task is to shoot space debris and sometimes enemy ships. Pick up upgrades to more effectively fight the impending danger and score the best final score. A local game mode for two is available. Where the two of you already have to destroy the asteroids and alien ships around you.
